

			OSDL README
			
			
This is the @OSDL_FULL_VERSION@ version of the OSDL (Object-oriented Simple DirectMedia Layer) library, released on @OSDL_RELEASE_DATE@ under the LGPL/GPL disjunctive bi-license, as stated in COPYING.LIB.

OSDL is a high level open source portable multimedia library, built upon Sam Lantinga's SDL. Its goal is to provide a high level C++ framework to ease game development.
 
The full documentation for OSDL, including troubleshooting section, is to be found at @OSDL_SF_URL@, notably at @OSDL_SF_VERSION_URL@ for everything specific to this @OSDL_VERSION@ version.

See also the INSTALL file for installation hints.

Have fun with OSDL !
